* * *

[![](http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5086/5216318522_71387d4e50_o.jpg)](http://www.flickr.com/photos/stilist/5216318522/)

Since the launch of the iOS App Store, <span class="company">Apple</span> has
made increasing use of its Apple ID system. Apple ID powers all the company’s
digital purchasing — [iTunes Store][itunes_store], [App Store][app_store], the
forthcoming [Mac App Store][mac_app_store], and the online
[Apple Store][apple_store]. [FaceTime][facetime] and the
[recently-made-free][ios_42] [Find My iPhone][find_my_iphone] services use it,
as do a [wide variety of other offerings][w_apple_id].

