## existing elements

* streaming
* data centers
* focus on portability
* increasingly powerful devices

## in progress

* abstract away file system: Spotlight, Dock, Launchpad (Lion)
* single-tasking (iOS, Lion full-screen)
* new free MobileMe account (Find My iPhone)
* same app, different platform (e.g. iWork)

## missing

* iOS file system?
* wireless sync
* large-scale data synchronization

## competitors

* Windows Live Mesh / ChromeOS
* Dropbox

## problems

* reluctant to fully embrace cloud
* network
* storage capability and cost
* setup times (new install)
* pricing
* consumer interest

